{"id":778,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":778,"title":"Jeremiah 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","Jeremiah sorrows greatly because of the sins of the people—They will be scattered among the nations and punished."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.1","order":"02.25.009.51370"},["b","1"],"Oh that my head were waters, and mine eyes a fountain of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"tears"],", that I might",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"weep"],"day and night for the slain of the daughter of my people!"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.2","order":"02.25.009.51371"},["b","2"],"Oh that I had in the wilderness a lodging place of wayfaring men; that I might leave my people, and go from them! for they",["i","be"],"all adulterers, an assembly of treacherous men."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.3","order":"02.25.009.51372"},["b","3"],"And they bend their tongues",["i","like"],"their bow",["i","for"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"lies"],": but they are not valiant for the truth upon the earth; for they proceed from evil to evil, and they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"know not"],"me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.4","order":"02.25.009.51373"},["b","4"],"Take ye heed every one of his neighbour, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"trust"],"ye not in any brother: for every brother will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"utterly supplant"],", and every neighbour will walk with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"slanders"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.5","order":"02.25.009.51374"},["b","5"],"And they will deceive every one his neighbour, and will not speak the truth: they have taught their tongue to speak",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"lies"],",",["i","and"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"weary themselves"],"to commit iniquity."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.6","order":"02.25.009.51375"},["b","6"],"Thine habitation",["i","is"],"in the midst of deceit; through deceit they refuse to know me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.7","order":"02.25.009.51376"},["b","7"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, Behold, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"melt"],"them, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"try"],"them; for how shall I do for the daughter of my people?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.8","order":"02.25.009.51377"},["b","8"],"Their tongue",["i","is as"],"an arrow shot out; it speaketh deceit:",["i","one"],"speaketh peaceably to his neighbour with his mouth, but in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"heart"],"he layeth his wait."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.9","order":"02.25.009.51378"},["b","9"],"¶Shall I not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"visit"],"them for these",["i","things?"],"saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": shall not my soul be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"avenged"],"on such a nation as this?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.10","order":"02.25.009.51379"},["b","10"],"For the mountains will I take up a weeping and wailing, and for the habitations of the wilderness a lamentation, because they are burned up, so that none can pass through",["i","them;"],"neither can",["i","men"],"hear the voice of the cattle; both the fowl of the heavens and the beast are fled; they are gone."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.11","order":"02.25.009.51380"},["b","11"],"And I will make Jerusalem heaps,",["i","and"],"a den of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"dragons"],"; and I will make the cities of Judah",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"desolate"],", without an inhabitant."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.12","order":"02.25.009.51381"},["b","12"],"¶Who",["i","is"],"the wise man, that may understand this? and",["i","who is he"],"to whom the mouth of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoken, that he may declare it, for what the land perisheth",["i","and"],"is burned up like a wilderness, that none passeth through?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.13","order":"02.25.009.51382"},["b","13"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"saith, Because they have forsaken my law which I set before them, and have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"obeyed"],"my voice, neither walked therein;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.14","order":"02.25.009.51383"},["b","14"],"But have walked after the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"imagination"],"of their own heart, and after",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Baalim"],", which their fathers taught them:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.15","order":"02.25.009.51384"},["b","15"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, the God of Israel; Behold, I will feed them,",["i","even"],"this people, with wormwood, and give them water of gall to drink."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.16","order":"02.25.009.51385"},["b","16"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"scatter"],"them also among the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"heathen"],", whom neither they nor their fathers have known: and I will send a sword after them, till I have consumed them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.17","order":"02.25.009.51386"},["b","17"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, Consider ye, and call for the mourning",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"women"],", that they may come; and send for cunning",["i","women,"],"that they may come:"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.18","order":"02.25.009.51387"},["b","18"],"And let them make haste, and take up a wailing for us, that our eyes may run down with tears, and our eyelids gush out with waters."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.19","order":"02.25.009.51388"},["b","19"],"For a voice of wailing is heard out of Zion, How are we spoiled! we are greatly confounded, because we have forsaken the land, because our dwellings have cast",["i","us"],"out."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.20","order":"02.25.009.51389"},["b","20"],"Yet hear the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", O ye women, and let your ear receive the word of his mouth, and teach your daughters wailing, and every one her neighbour lamentation."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.21","order":"02.25.009.51390"},["b","21"],"For death is come up into our windows,",["i","and"],"is entered into our palaces, to cut off the children from without,",["i","and"],"the young men from the streets."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.22","order":"02.25.009.51391"},["b","22"],"Speak, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Even the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"carcases"],"of men shall fall as dung upon the open field, and as the handful after the harvestman, and none shall gather",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.23","order":"02.25.009.51392"},["b","23"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Let not the wise",["i","man"],"glory in his wisdom, neither let the mighty",["i","man"],"glory in his might, let not the rich",["i","man"],"glory in his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"riches"],":"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.24","order":"02.25.009.51393"},["b","24"],"But let him that glorieth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"glory"],"in this, that he understandeth and knoweth me, that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"which exercise lovingkindness, judgment, and righteousness, in the earth: for in these",["i","things"],"I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"delight"],", saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.25","order":"02.25.009.51394"},["b","25"],"¶Behold, the days come, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that I will punish all",["i","them which are"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"circumcised"],"with the uncircumcised;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.26","order":"02.25.009.51395"},["b","26"],"Egypt, and Judah, and Edom, and the children of Ammon, and Moab, and all",["i","that are"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"utmost"],"corners, that dwell in the wilderness: for all",["i","these"],"nations",["i","are"],"uncircumcised, and all the house of Israel",["i","are"],"uncircumcised in the heart."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.1a","order":"02.25.009.51396"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.1b","order":"02.25.009.51398"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/despair"},"TG Despair"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.3a","order":"02.25.009.51400"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/64.3"},"Ps. 64:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.3b","order":"02.25.009.51402"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/17.3"},"John 17:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.16"},"D&C 101:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.4a","order":"02.25.009.51404"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.5.5-6"},"Micah 7:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.31"},"2 Ne. 28:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.19"},"D&C 1:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.4b","order":"02.25.009.51406"},["b","4b"],["span.small","OR"],"consistently deceive."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.4c","order":"02.25.009.51408"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/slander"},"TG Slander"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.5a","order":"02.25.009.51410"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"TG Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.5b","order":"02.25.009.51412"},["b","5b"],["span.small","OR"],"are impatient."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.7a","order":"02.25.009.51414"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.7.7-9"},"2 Ne. 23:7 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.41"},"D&C 133:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.7b","order":"02.25.009.51416"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.25.25-26"},"Isa. 1:25 (25–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2.2-3"},"Mal. 3:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.8a","order":"02.25.009.51418"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.9a","order":"02.25.009.51420"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.1"},"Mosiah 12:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.50"},"D&C 124:50"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.9b","order":"02.25.009.51422"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.9.9,29"},"Jer. 5:9 (9, 29)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.22"},"44:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.11a","order":"02.25.009.51424"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"jackals."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.11b","order":"02.25.009.51426"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.7"},"Isa. 1:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8"},"2 Ne. 13:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.13a","order":"02.25.009.51428"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.14a","order":"02.25.009.51430"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.18"},"1 Ne. 12:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.14b","order":"02.25.009.51432"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/33.3"},"2 Chr. 33:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.16a","order":"02.25.009.51434"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.16b","order":"02.25.009.51436"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heathen"},"TG Heathen"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.17a","order":"02.25.009.51438"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.22a","order":"02.25.009.51440"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.33"},"Jer. 7:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.23a","order":"02.25.009.51442"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.24a","order":"02.25.009.51444"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.31"},"1 Cor. 1:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.17.15-18"},"2 Cor. 10:17 (15–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.36.36-37"},"Alma 26:36 (36–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.24b","order":"02.25.009.51446"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.18"},"Micah 7:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.25a","order":"02.25.009.51448"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/circumcision"},"TG Circumcision"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.26a","order":"02.25.009.51450"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.23"},"Jer. 25:23"],"."]]}
